1.00	Stantz	Raymond Stantz	Raymond "Ray" Stantz, Ph.D., is a fictional scientist and member of the Ghostbusters, appearing in the films Ghostbusters, Ghostbusters II, and Casper (played by Dan Aykroyd) and in the animated television series The Real Ghostbusters (voiced by Frank Welker). He is one of the three doctors of parapsychology on the team, along with Dr. Peter Venkman and Dr. Egon Spengler.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/50/Ray_GB1.jpg/250px-Ray_GB1.jpg
